HEADWORD: Covenanting
<hw>Cov"e*nant*ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Belonging to a covenant.
Specifically, belonging to the Scotch Covenanters.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Be they <qex>covenanting</qex> traitors,⟦br⟧
Or the brood of false Argyle?</q> <rj><qau>Aytoun.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Covenantor</ent>⟦br⟧
